ona</cite>, mayo de 2019, págs. 67, 68.</p></li><li data-marker=16. id=note16><p data-aid=141770803 id=note16_p1>Véase Dallin H. Oaks, “La espiritualidad”, <cite>Liahona</cite>, enero de 1986, pág. 48.</p></li><li data-marker=17. id=note17><p data-aid=141770810 id=note17_p1>“Más santidad dame”, <em>Himnos</em>, nro. 71.</p></li></ol></footer></div></article><div class=startHandle-2o_6p touch-action=none></div><div class=endHandle-wg4Dv touch-action=none></div></div></section></section><div class=mobileNav-1qobD><a class="mobileIcon-3ABLr mobilePrev-1Jf8d" href="/study/liahona/2019/11/46nelson?lang=spa"><button dir=ltr class="iconButton--V5Iv navButton-WGhZC"><span class=hiddenTitleText-2SahY></span><svg style=width:1.625rem;height:1.625rem viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns=http://www.w3.org/2000/svg role=presentation> <path fill=currentColor d="M4.438 10.856a.77.77 0 0 1 .097-.117l6.709-6.71a.755.755 0 0 1 1.065-.003.751.751 0 0 1-.005 1.064L6.6 10.795h11.647c.403 0 .744.335.744.75 0 .417-.333.75-.744.75H6.565l5.74 5.739a.755.755 0 0 1 .004 1.065.751.751 0 0 1-1.065-.005l-6.71-6.709a.757.757 0 0 1-.127-.169.755.755 0 0 1-.416-.671c0-.31.184-.574.447-.689z"> </path></svg></button></a><a class="mobileIcon-3ABLr mobileNext-1J33m" href="/study/liahona/2019/11/52boom?lang=spa"><button style=transform:scale(-1) class="iconButton--V5Iv navButton-WGhZC"><span class=hiddenTitleText-2SahY></span><svg style=width:1.625rem;height:1.625rem viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns=http://www.w3.org/2000/svg role=presentation> <path fill=currentColor d="M4.438 10.856a.77.77 0 0 1 .097-.117l6.709-6.71a.755.755 0 0 1 1.065-.003.751.751 0 0 1-.005 1.064L6.6 10.795h11.647c.403 0 .744.335.744.75 0 .417-.333.75-.744.75H6.565l5.74 5.739a.755.755 0 0 1 .004 1.065.751.751 0 0 1-1.065-.005l-6.71-6.709a.757.757 0 0 1-.127-.169.755.755 0 0 1-.416-.671c0-.31.184-.574.447-.689z"> </path></svg></button></a></div></div><aside class="sidePanel-3uL9p relatedContentPanel-2wEUz"><div class="innerPanel-3gbqC innerPanel-32K4